==English==

===Pronunciation===
*bû(r)th, /bɜː(r)θ/, /b3:(r)T/
*:'''Homophones''': [[berth]]

===Noun===
'''birth'''  (''plural:'' [[births]])

# (''uncountable'') The process of [[childbearing]].<!-- #2 between current 1&2: an instance of birth (countable), #1 is uncountable -->
# (''countable'') A beginning or start; a point of origin.
# (''uncountable'') The circumstances of one's background, ancestry, or upbringing ''of [[noble]] birth''.

